  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/5f46ad37ccd12ae9f47a46a81e4995a1.webp?t=1741413186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/5f46ad37ccd12ae9f47a46a81e4995a1.poster.avif?t=1741413186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=500 height=133 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐️DA-DA-DA-DADA!⭐️ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BULLIES OF MIDDLING MIDDLE SCHOOL, YOU'RE IN FOR A SURPRISE!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's Halloween Spirit Week and even gloomy Tabbie is ready for some fun.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But when her nemesis, Eden, (the <u>WORST</u> kind of eighth grade boy), steals her thunder, everything goes horribly wrong. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Luckily, a magical pixie comes to Tabbie's aid and grants her the power <u>WHACK THE SH⭐️T out of anyone in her way!</u>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > While her tiny handler expects her to use her new powers for good, this magical girl has other plans in mind: ⭐️  <strong>REVENGE!!! </strong>⭐️   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*********************************************************************************</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>This Magical Girl is a B⭐️tch</strong> is a comedic visual novel inspired by magical girl staples such as Shugo Chara and Card Captor Sakura. </i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/6bc1e1cf28c6b2a3cc7d38ae7375614d.webp?t=1741413186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/6bc1e1cf28c6b2a3cc7d38ae7375614d.poster.avif?t=1741413186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=500 height=133 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐️ <strong>UNCONVENTIONAL MAGICAL GIRL:</strong> <i>Tabbie Bones' magical misadventures thus far, detailed in 24k words, 15 CGs, and 2 animated transformation sequences <strong>(~3 hours of playtime)</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐️ <strong>FULLY VOICED CAST:</strong> <i>Every student and faculty member of Middling Middle School has a voice (and they're going to use it!)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐️ <strong>BRANCHING CHOICES, STICKER ACHIEVEMENTS, SECRET ENDINGS:</strong> <i>Actions have consequences...especially when you're a magical girl!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐️ <strong>EXPRESSIVE CHARACTER SPRITES:</strong> <i>200+ hand-drawn expressions and poses meticulously coded to dance across the screen at your command.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐️<strong>ORIGINAL EARWORMS:</strong> <i>Catchy original soundtrack to accompany Tabbie's saddest, maddest, and baddest moments.<br></i>*Full game statistics will be available at launch </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/3bea208005de4551a728bcfd4ff13226.webp?t=1741413186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/3bea208005de4551a728bcfd4ff13226.poster.avif?t=1741413186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=500 height=133 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/9f2de2a4ed26fdb70b660312482d5546.avif?t=1741413186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras_big/9f2de2a4ed26fdb70b660312482d5546.avif?t=1741413186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/c2d07e23ba49cd8e9bd06f31105ec604.avif?t=1741413186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras_big/c2d07e23ba49cd8e9bd06f31105ec604.avif?t=1741413186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/b0a0ba6be18dfde5576b34b732392980.avif?t=1741413186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras_big/b0a0ba6be18dfde5576b34b732392980.avif?t=1741413186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/d57192d01e57ac9aa2e881ba5b85dfeb.avif?t=1741413186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras_big/d57192d01e57ac9aa2e881ba5b85dfeb.avif?t=1741413186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras/86a5ba03782f17d9b39bbba76a7feea8.avif?t=1741413186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810830/extras_big/86a5ba03782f17d9b39bbba76a7feea8.avif?t=1741